OL,3,CFour charged two years after death of
OL,4,Cman in crash
OL,6,FFour people have been charged with
OL,7,Fmanslaughter over the death of a man
OL,8,Fin a car crash almost two years ago.
OL,10,FMackenzie Ball, who was 20, was a
OL,11,Fpassenger in a Land Rover which
OL,12,Fcollided with a Subaru Forester on
OL,13,FMorthen Road in Rotherham in June 2024.
OL,15,FHe died at the scene.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
