OL,3,CFour charged two years after death of
OL,4,Cman in crash
OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Police initially
OL,7,Flaunched a murder investigation but
OL,8,Fhave now charged four Sheffield men
OL,9,Fwith manslaughter: Owen Cocksedge, 19,
OL,10,FKowen Pitts, 21, of Jaunty Avenue,
OL,11,FAdam Platts, 20, of Newbould Crescent,
OL,12,Fand Deacon Blake, 18, of Jaunty Avenue.
OL,14,FCocksedge is also charged with causing
OL,15,Fdeath by dangerous driving and while
OL,16,Fbanned and uninsured, two counts of
OL,17,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,18,Fdriving and dangerous driving.
OL,20,FBlake is charged with causing grievous
OL,21,Fbodily harm.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
